column2: SELECT U.up_id, S.* FROM #upLoad U CROSS APPLY (SELECT Objid FROM dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (U.up_ra , U.up_dec , U.up_sep) ) S SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, cast (str (p.ra, #, #) as float) as ra, cast (str (p.[dec], #, #) as float) as dec FROM ..PhotoObj AS p JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE (p.type = # OR p.type = #) ORDER BY x.up_id
